        <abstract>
            <p>Neither he nor [Francis Darwin] intends publishing on inheritance.</p> 
<p>They are working on physiology of plants [<hi rend="italic">Movement in plants</hi>], but will not print for a year.</p>  
<p>Thinks JVC’s new journal [<hi rend="italic">Zoologische Anzeiger</hi>] will be of great use to students of zoology.</p> 
        </abstract>
